// #taxon[Taxon]
#title[Assuming enough Universes]

We will assume that for every finite list of of types in context $Gamma_1$ trough $Gamma_n$ there exists a universe $Uu$ that contains these types.
See Postulate 6.2.1 in #local("008M")[Introduction to Homotopy Type Theory]
